
<div class="jumbotron">
  <h1>Sign in</h1>

  <div class="row form-horizontal">
    <div class="span6 offset3">
      <%= form_for(:session, url: sessions_path) do |f| %>

      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.label :email, "Email",:class=>"col-sm-2 col-sm-offset-3 control-label"%>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <%= f.text_field :email,:class=>"form-control" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <%= f.label :password, "Password",:class=>"col-xs-2 col-sm-2 col-sm-offset-3 control-label"%>
        <div class="col-sm-4">
          <%= f.password_field :password,:class=>"form-control" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-offset-4">
        <%= f.submit "Sign in", class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %>
      </div>
        <p class="col-sm-offset-1 col-xs-offset-2">New user? <%= link_to "Sign up now!", new_circle_path %></p>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <div class="well">
    <div class="page-header">
      <h2>Updates</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="list-group">
      <ul>
        <li>2016/4/12 ラウンドのback機能を修正しました</li>
        <li>練習の途中でプレーヤーを追加すると連続でその人が入ってしまうバグを修正しました</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
